hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I've just graduated pharmaron beijing limited John Gosden has given The Fugue a first preference of the Turf over a mile and a half, traditionally Europe’s strongest event, on Saturday-week rather than the Filly & Mare Turf over a mile and a quarter in which she came unstuck last year. With a clear run she would almost certainly have won and, ever since, Gosden has been keener on the Turf because it is less reliant on a good draw.
